# Paths published to the public almanak-sdk mirror (allowlist).
# One path per line. Directories should end with /
# Blank lines and comments (starting with #) are ignored.
# Paths NOT listed here are NEVER published.
#
# This is an ALLOWLIST. It is intentionally explicit so that any new top-level
# file or directory added to the private repo does NOT leak to the public
# mirror unless it is also added here.

# --- Top-level metadata ---
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
CONTRIBUTING.md
CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
SECURITY.md
PYPI.md
LICENSE

